Ranking 2024

Featuring 501 cities across 62 countries on 6 continents, the TomTom Traffic Index evaluates cities around the world by their average travel time and congestion level, providing free access to high-quality and useful information. Whether you're a driver, pedestrian, city planner, car and policymaker, the index can help you tackle everyday traffic challenges.
